txt.en: Their leader must be within this heavily guarded tomb
'The Iron Crown will have its revenge!'
'I shall unlock the secrets within these tombs!'
<u>Houses of Rest</u>\n\qAncient moon-letters are waiting to be uncovered by those who brave the long forgotten halls, deep within the Pit of Stonejaws.\q
The forces of Stonejaws have already reached Adkhât-zahhar!
Enemy forces have completely overtaken the Houses of Rest!
